You just want to know when your code is doneâ€¦  
and have a beer while waiting. ğŸ»

## Example with timing options

```python
from brewbar import bar
import time

for _ in bar(
    range(200),
    eta=True,
    elapsed=True,
    rate=True,
    ascii=True,
):
    time.sleep(0.05)
```